{"type": "article", "id": 30220, "title": "包含冰山的矮桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160727204445QXKd4PMvnezATiya.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>炎炎夏日，由法国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.harow.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Harow</a> 推出的矮桌 <a href=\"http://www.harow.fr/iceberg.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Iceberg</a> 或许会让你感受到一股凉意。这些方方正正的矮桌有着如同冰块一样光滑的表面，采用玻璃纤维和环氧树脂手工制作而成，Harow 希望通过这个独特的创意“冻结”住极地那种深邃的美感，同时展现出人类活动对于环境以及子孙的影响。Iceberg 均在位于巴黎的工作坊内进行加工，每一件都至少要花费一个月的时间，限量 100 件出售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272045001mBkRuUElCTJ4esx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727204500koMFICbmyqjO7zKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727204501ptQ4EHGi23on7ycf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727204501hyvJkVmpTaunFzLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}